- Come on, Julia.

885
00:56:13,036 --> 00:56:14,162
She bailed on us.

886
00:56:14,246 --> 00:56:16,373
We don't have any money, genius.

887
00:56:16,456 --> 00:56:18,208
Well, I have money, so...

888
00:56:18,917 --> 00:56:20,544
You have money
so we should do what you want?

889
00:56:21,086 --> 00:56:22,254
You got something to say?

890
00:56:22,880 --> 00:56:25,757
You know,
I bet your dad is a senator

891
00:56:25,841 --> 00:56:27,426
and your mom
sits on the board at the Met.

892
00:56:27,509 --> 00:56:29,720
And you summer in the Hamptons
next to Martha Stewart.

893
00:56:29,803 --> 00:56:31,722
So sad about Martha Stewart.

894
00:56:35,100 --> 00:56:36,518
My parents are in Beijing...

895
00:56:36,602 --> 00:56:37,853
where my dad
is raking in a ton of money

896
