The housekeeper.

902
00:56:50,032 --> 00:56:52,034
Well, on the upside, no curfew.

903
00:56:53,118 --> 00:56:54,620
I bet you have
your own room at least.

904
00:56:55,412 --> 00:56:58,415
I live with my dad and his wife
and their kid.

905
00:56:58,498 --> 00:57:00,751
- What about your mom?
- She's...

906
00:57:02,336 --> 00:57:03,503
not really around.

907
00:57:03,587 --> 00:57:04,880
She bailed on you?

908
00:57:05,839 --> 00:57:08,050
Right. So, diner?

909
00:57:09,426 --> 00:57:11,178
We spend some of Mattie's
daddy's pollution money?

910
00:57:11,261 --> 00:57:12,262
Yay.

911
00:57:12,346 --> 00:57:14,431
I'm going to order
everything on the menu.

912
00:57:17,267 --> 00:57:18,435
Julia, you in?

913
00:57:20,103 --> 00:57:21,396
Hey.

914
00:57:21,480 --> 00:57:23,065
We have
to take care of ourselves.

915
00:57:30,572 --> 00:57:31,573
Yeah.

916
00:57:33,909 --> 00:57:34,910
You're right.

917
00:57:36,620 --> 00:57:37,746
Let's go do this.

918
00:57:39,998 --> 00:57:41,416
She's kind of cute
when she's mad.

919
00:57:41,500 --> 00:57:42,668
I heard that.

920
00:57:44,461 --> 00:57:46,797
You are making
the right decision, Julia.

921
