923
00:57:51,093 --> 00:57:53,929
God! I knew
we shouldn't have done this.

924
00:57:58,558 --> 00:57:59,685
Shit.

925
00:57:59,768 --> 00:58:01,103
Do you think there's ticks?

926
00:58:02,980 --> 00:58:03,981
Can we walk

927
