931
00:58:15,283 --> 00:58:16,284
Ow! Shit!

932
00:58:20,288 --> 00:58:22,541
Okay. Don't talk
to anybody except to order.

933
00:58:23,125 --> 00:58:24,126
We're in the middle of nowhere.

934
00:58:24,209 --> 00:58:25,544
No one's gonna
track us down here.

935
00:58:25,627 --> 00:58:27,337
Just don't make eye contact.

936
00:58:27,921 --> 00:58:29,589
I hope they have cherry pie.

937
00:58:40,517 --> 00:58:41,852
Let's sit at the bar.

938
00:58:48,942 --> 00:58:49,943
There you go.

939
00:58:51,445 --> 00:58:52,446
Here.

940
