00:59:44,581 --> 00:59:46,374
Come on. You know you want to.

958
00:59:46,458 --> 00:59:47,459
No.

959
00:59:47,542 --> 00:59:50,128
- This is not a good idea.
- Okay, wait, wait, wait.

960
00:59:50,212 --> 00:59:51,421
- What're you doing?
- Yeah, what are you doing?

961
00:59:51,505 --> 00:59:52,798
Just hold on a second.

962
00:59:52,881 --> 00:59:53,924
What is this?

963
00:59:54,007 --> 00:59:55,008
Do you want the Reuben?

964
00:59:56,301 --> 00:59:58,470
It's just
a little confidence boost.

965
00:59:58,553 --> 01:00:00,180
This isn't really my style.

966
01:00:01,807 --> 01:00:03,433
So what? You look cute. Come on.

967
01:00:03,517 --> 01:00:05,936
This is not a good idea.
Seriously, guys.

968
01:00:06,645 --> 01:00:07,646
Okay.

969
01:00:07,729 --> 01:00:09,147
Hi. Hey, guys.

970
01:00:09,231 --> 01:00:10,941
- I'm Mattie. This is Julia.
- Oh, hey. Good.

971
01:00:11,024 --> 01:00:12,317
- Can we sit?
- Yeah, of course.

972
01:00:12,400 --> 01:00:13,819
We've been
saving these seats for you.

973
01:00:13,902 --> 01:00:15,028
Awesome.

974
01:00:16,029 --> 01:00:17,405
Oh, hey, what's up?
How you doin'?

975
01:00:17,489 --> 01:00:18,490
Nice to meet you too.

976
01:00:18,573 --> 01:00:19,574
<i>...for your information.</i>

977
01:00:19,658 --> 01:00:21,368
