Girls!

991
01:01:19,384 --> 01:01:20,385
Girls!

992
01:01:25,015 --> 01:01:26,266
Oh, God damn it.

993
01:01:44,284 --> 01:01:45,285
Girls!

994
01:01:54,044 --> 01:01:55,629
Let's go. Let's go!

995
01:01:56,129 --> 01:01:57,839
Don't even pretend
that you're cooler than Britney.

996
01:01:57,923 --> 01:01:58,924
I know you know the words.

997
01:01:59,007 --> 01:02:00,926
- Come on, get up here.
- You should get up there.

998
01:02:01,009 --> 01:02:02,844
So much
for not attracting attention.

999
01:02:12,812 --> 01:02:14,648
No. Please. Please, stop.

1000
01:02:14,731 --> 01:02:16,233
Don't touch me, okay?

1001
01:02:16,316 --> 01:02:17,567
Can you...

1002
01:02:17,651 --> 01:02:19,736
What are you doing?

1003
01:02:19,819 --> 01:02:20,946
- What are you...
- What is that?

1004
01:02:21,029 --> 01:02:22,364
We have to go.

1005
01:02:26,034 --> 01:02:27,160
I'm so sorry.

1006
01:02:29,996 --> 01:02:30,997
Get down!

1007
01:02:32,374 --> 01:02:33,959
- This isn't what you think.
- Get your stuff.

1008
01:02:34,042 --> 01:02:35,085
You left us.

1009
01:02:36,544 --> 01:02:37,754
I'm so sorry.

1010
01:02:40,507 --> 01:02:41,758
Julia!

1011
01:02:41,841 --> 01:02:42,842
Julia!

1012
01:02:43,969 --> 01:02:44,970
Julia, get back!

1013
01:02:56,231 --> 01:02:57,232
Come on!

1014
01:02:57,315 --> 01:02:58,441
No! Mattie!

1015
01:02:59,567 --> 01:03:00,568
No.

1016
01:03:47,657 --> 01:03:49,451
<i>This track is going to be huge.</i>

1017
01:03:49,534 --> 01:03:51,745
<i>Are you in the zone?
This is Britney Spears.</i>

1018
01:03:54,956 --> 01:03:56,624
Let's try that again.

1019
01:04:07,052 --> 01:04:09,846
I love this song.

1020
01:04:13,350 --> 01:04:14,351
