1532
01:41:54,108 --> 01:41:55,610
What makes you so sure?

1533
01:42:02,950 --> 01:42:04,952
Come on. Come on, come on.

1534
01:42:05,036 --> 01:42:06,412
You're just like your mother.

1535
01:42:06,495 --> 01:42:08,247
Yes, I am.

1536
01:42:31,020 --> 01:42:32,980
You've been trying
to change your future.

1537
01:42:34,732 --> 01:42:36,984
But the girls
were never your future.

1538
01:42:38,653 --> 01:42:39,695
I was.

1539
01:42:53,751 --> 01:42:55,628
No!

1540
01:43:18,567 --> 01:43:20,528
No. Cassie!

1541
01:44:14,290 --> 01:44:15,583
She's not breathing.

1542
01:44:15,666 --> 01:44:17,251
- Her heart's not beating.
- We know what to do.

1543
01:44:18,043 --> 01:44:19,044
Beginning compressions.

1544
01:44:20,171 --> 01:44:22,590
Interlock your fingers.
Come back, Cassie.

1545
01:44:22,673 --> 01:44:23,966
Come on, guys. Come on!

1546
01:44:25,551 --> 01:44:27,094
Keep going. We don't stop.

1547
01:44:28,012 --> 01:44:29,013
Come on, Cassie.

1548
01:44:30,097 --> 01:44:31,307
I'm getting a little tired.

1549
01:44:31,390 --> 01:44:32,725
Okay. I'm right here.

1550
01:44:33,809 --> 01:44:35,227
Cassie, wake up! Please.

1551
01:44:35,311 --> 01:44:36,979
- Cassie!
- Come back, Cassie.

1552
01:44:38,814 --> 01:44:40,608
We're here, Cassie.
We're not leaving you.

1553
01:44:41,317 --> 01:44:43,235
Cassie, you got this.
Please. I need you. Please.

1554
01:44:45,571 --> 01:44:46,781
Oh, my God!

1555
01:44:47,490 --> 01:44:48,491
Cassie.

1556
01:44:49,825 --> 01:44:51,410
- It's okay.
- It's okay. It's okay.

1557
01:44:51,494 --> 01:44:52,495
Oh, my God. We did it.

1558
01:44:57,500 --> 01:44:58,751
We did it.

1559
01:45:19,855 --> 01:45:20,856
Hi.

1560
01:45:23,317 --> 01:45:24,568
Hello.

1561
01:45:24,652 --> 01:45:25,653
Hi.

1562
01:45:27,947 --> 01:45:29,657
Oh, he's perfect.

1563
01:45:30,533 --> 01:45:31,534
He is.

1564
01:45:32,034 --> 01:45:33,661
- He's perfect.
- Yeah.

1565
01:45:41,377 --> 01:45:42,670
We're still here, Cassie.

1566
01:45:43,462 --> 01:45:44,964
Yeah. We're not leaving you.

1567
01:45:45,965 --> 01:45:46,966
I wouldn't be here

1568
01:45:47,049 --> 01:45:48,467
if it weren't
for the three of you.

1569
01:45:49,093 --> 01:45:50,469
Right back at ya.

1570
01:45:50,970 --> 01:45:51,971
Ben said to tell you

1571
01:45:52,054 --> 01:45:53,472
that the baby
is doing really well.

1572
01:45:54,265 --> 01:45:55,850
And he's loving being an uncle.

1573
01:45:56,976 --> 01:45:59,979
Yeah. All the fun
and none of the responsibility.

1574
01:46:01,063 --> 01:46:02,565
That's what he thinks.

1575
01:46:05,776 --> 01:46:08,112
Are you all immediate family?

1576
01:46:08,571 --> 01:46:09,780
Yes.

1577
01:46:10,990 --> 01:46:12,408
They're all mine.

1578
01:46:19,498 --> 01:46:21,000
Can we get you anything?

1579
01:46:21,083 --> 01:46:22,084
No.

1580
01:46:23,002 --> 01:46:25,087
I have everything I need
right here.

1581
01:46:54,742 --> 01:46:55,743
No.

1582
01:46:59,330 --> 01:47:02,541
You left your junk mail
downstairs again.

1583
01:47:02,625 --> 01:47:05,794
And we got takeout.
But we didn't know...

1584
01:47:05,878 --> 01:47:07,504
Kung Pao chicken is perfect.

1585
01:47:07,588 --> 01:47:08,881
How'd you know?

1586
01:47:09,632 --> 01:47:10,716
Bless you, Anya.

1587
01:47:10,799 --> 01:47:11,800
What?

1588
01:47:14,345 --> 01:47:15,346
Thank you.

1589
01:47:19,183 --> 01:47:20,184
Mattie!

1590
01:47:20,267 --> 01:47:22,686
What? I told you I'm starving.

1591
01:47:22,770 --> 01:47:24,438
And I told you guys
that you wouldn't...

1592
01:47:24,521 --> 01:47:26,273
...wouldn't like you
if you were hangry.

1593
01:47:26,357 --> 01:47:28,150
Well, you wouldn't, so...

1594
01:47:29,443 --> 01:47:30,444
How's your eyesight?

1595
01:47:30,986 --> 01:47:32,655
I can see better
than I ever have.

1596
01:47:32,738 --> 01:47:33,739
Oh, yeah?

1597
01:47:34,365 --> 01:47:36,659
Can you see us in the future?

1598
01:47:37,576 --> 01:47:38,702
Yes.

1599
01:47:39,954 --> 01:47:41,163
I can see you.

1600
01:47:43,082 --> 01:47:45,042
<i>Standing up
for what you believe.</i>

1601
01:47:50,673 --> 01:47:51,882
<i>Never giving up.</i>

1602
01:47:57,429 --> 01:48:00,349
<i>Discovering you were always
more powerful than you thought.</i>

1603
01:48:02,101 --> 01:48:03,894
Nothing I didn't already know.

1604
01:48:06,605 --> 01:48:08,023
I don't know about you two...

1605
01:48:08,607 --> 01:48:10,818
but that totally
makes sense to me.

1606
01:48:11,402 --> 01:48:13,320
- What? I'm serious.
- Wow.

1607
01:48:15,906 --> 01:48:17,408
What? I'm being serious.

1608
01:48:21,328 --> 01:48:23,664
Oh, wow. Okay. Wow.

1609
01:48:32,965 --> 01:48:34,508
<i>Whatever the future holds...</i>

1610
01:48:40,556 --> 01:48:41,765
<i>we'll be ready.</i>

1611
01:48:44,059 --> 01:48:45,936
<i>And you know the best thing
about the future?</i>

1612
01:48:48,063 --> 01:48:49,982
<i>It hasn't happened yet.</i>

